#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Positions et analyses** : ``position`` (les positions, dÃĐdupliquÃĐes), "
"``analysis`` (les donnÃĐes d'analyse associÃĐes) et ``comment`` (les "
"commentaires)."
msgstr ""
"**Positions and analyses**: ``position`` (the positions, deduplicated), "
"``analysis`` (the associated analysis data) and ``comment`` (the "
"comments)."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:40
msgid ""
"**Matchs** : ``match``, ``game``, ``move`` et ``move_analysis`` stockent "
"les matchs importÃĐs, leurs parties, leurs coups et l'analyse de chaque "
"coup."
msgstr ""
"**Matches**: ``match``, ``game``, ``move`` and ``move_analysis`` store "
"the imported matches, their games, their moves and the analysis of each "
"move."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:43
msgid ""
"**Collections** : ``collection`` et ``collection_position`` (table de "
"liaison) regroupent des positions choisies manuellement."
msgstr ""
"**Collections**: ``collection`` and ``collection_position`` (link table) "
"group together manually chosen positions."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:46
msgid "**Tournois** : ``tournament`` regroupe des matchs en tournois."
msgstr "**Tournaments**: ``tournament`` groups matches into tournaments."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:48
msgid ""
"**RÃĐpÃĐtition espacÃĐe (Anki)** : ``anki_deck``, ``anki_card`` et "
"``anki_review_log`` gÃĻrent les paquets, les cartes et le journal des "
"rÃĐvisions (algorithme FSRS)."
msgstr ""
"**Spaced repetition (Anki)**: ``anki_deck``, ``anki_card`` and "
"``anki_review_log`` manage the decks, the cards and the review log (FSRS "
"algorithm)."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:52
msgid ""
"**Historique et divers** : ``command_history`` et ``search_history`` "
"conservent l'historique des commandes et des recherches, "
"``filter_library`` la bibliothÃĻque de filtres, et ``metadata`` les "
"mÃĐtadonnÃĐes de la base (dont la version du schÃĐma)."
msgstr ""
"**History and miscellaneous**: ``command_history`` and ``search_history``"
" keep the history of commands and searches, ``filter_library`` the filter"
" library, and ``metadata`` the database metadata (including the schema "
"version)."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:58
msgid "Principes de conception"
msgstr "Design principles"

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:60
msgid ""
"Ã partir du schÃĐma 2.0.0, plusieurs choix de conception accÃĐlÃĻrent la "
"recherche et rÃĐduisent la taille du fichier :"
msgstr ""
"From schema 2.0.0 onwards, several design choices speed up searches and "
"reduce the file size:"

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:63
msgid ""
"**DÃĐduplication des positions** : chaque position porte un hash de "
"Zobrist et un index unique, de sorte qu'une mÃŠme position rencontrÃĐe dans"
" plusieurs imports n'est stockÃĐe qu'une seule fois."
msgstr ""
"**Position deduplication**: each position carries a Zobrist hash and a "
"unique index, so that the same position encountered across several "
"imports is stored only once."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:67
msgid ""
"**Colonnes de filtrage dÃĐnormalisÃĐes** : des critÃĻres frÃĐquemment "
"recherchÃĐs (type de dÃĐcision, dÃĐs, diffÃĐrence de course, pions sortis, "
"pions arriÃĐrÃĐs, erreur de coup ou de videau, chances de gainâĶ) sont "
"prÃĐcalculÃĐs en colonnes dÃĐdiÃĐes pour un filtrage rapide."
msgstr ""
"**Denormalised filter columns**: frequently searched criteria (decision "
"type, dice, race difference, checkers borne off, back checkers, checker-"
"play or cube error, chances of winning, etc.) are precomputed into "
"dedicated columns for fast filtering."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:72
msgid ""
"**PrÃĐfiltre par bitboards** : des colonnes d'occupation et de masques de "
"points permettent un prÃĐfiltre entier trÃĻs rapide lors des recherches de "
"motifs de structure."
msgstr ""
"**Bitboard prefilter**: occupancy and point-mask columns enable a very "
"fast integer prefilter when searching for structure patterns."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:76
msgid ""
"**Stockage compact** : les positions sont encodÃĐes de faÃ§on compacte et "
"les donnÃĐes d'analyse sont compressÃĐes (zlib), ce qui rÃĐduit fortement la"
" taille du fichier."
msgstr ""
"**Compact storage**: positions are encoded compactly and analysis data is"
" compressed (zlib), which greatly reduces the file size."

#: ../../source/annexe_db_scheme.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Journalisation WAL** : le mode WAL et des PRAGMA ajustÃĐs amÃĐliorent les"
" performances en lecture et en ÃĐcriture."
msgstr ""
"**WAL journaling**: WAL mode and tuned PRAGMAs improve read and write "
"performance."

